    "title": "Signal and/or RPC call to re-read config file",
    "body": "It would be handy in certain circumstances to be able to update the config file and then ask bitcoind to parse it again (when updating rpcallowip filters, for example). An RPC command like \"readconfig\" would be good. Trapping for a SIGHUP on Unix would be cool, too.\n",
